title: High schools with girls athletics programs in the U.S. by sport 2009 to 2019
summary: The given chart is of multi-line type with 10 lines namely Basketball, Track and Field - Outdoor, Volleyball, Softball - Fast Pitch, Cross Country, Soccer, Tennis, Golf, Swimming and Diving, and Competitive Spirit Squads. The y axis represents Number of high schools and the x axis represents Year.
